<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Privacidade — Lista de Compras</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <style>
    .privacy-page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: clamp(32px, 6vw, 72px) clamp(16px, 4vw, 32px);
    }
    .privacy-inner {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .privacy-hero {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .privacy-shield {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .privacy-hero-text h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .privacy-hero-text p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* ── Section label ── */
    .section-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    /* ── Data grid ── */
    .data-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .data-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      padding: 16px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .data-card-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      background: var(--accent-light);
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .data-card-name {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }
    .data-card-desc {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* ── Info row ── */
    .info-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .info-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    .info-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .info-card h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .info-card p, .info-card li {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .info-card ul { padding-left: 16px; }
    .info-card li { margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .info-card code {
      font-size: 11px;
      background: var(--surface-alt);
      padding: 1px 5px;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }
    .no-share {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    /* ── Rights cards ── */
    .rights-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .right-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .right-card-num {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .right-card-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .right-card-desc {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    /* ── Actions ── */
    .privacy-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="privacy-page">
    <div class="privacy-inner">

      <!-- Hero -->
      <div class="privacy-hero">
        <div class="privacy-shield">
          <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            <polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="privacy-hero-text">
          <h1>Política de Privacidade</h1>
          <p>Lista de Compras · Última atualização: 2026-05-20</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- O que coletamos -->
      <p class="section-label">O que armazenamos</p>
      <div class="data-grid">
        <div class="data-card">
          <div class="data-card-icon">
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="data-card-name">E-mail</div>
          <div class="data-card-desc">Identifica sua conta via Google OAuth</div>
        </div>
        <div class="data-card">
          <div class="data-card-icon">
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H8a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="data-card-name">Nome</div>
          <div class="data-card-desc">Exibido na interface do aplicativo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="data-card">
          <div class="data-card-icon">
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="data-card-name">ID Google</div>
          <div class="data-card-desc">Pseudônimo técnico, não revela identidade</div>
        </div>
        <div class="data-card">
          <div class="data-card-icon">
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V6l-3-4z"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="data-card-name">Lista de itens</div>
          <div class="data-card-desc">Conteúdo que você adiciona às listas</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Cookies + Base legal -->
      <p class="section-label">Como usamos</p>
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>Cookies</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><code>access_token</code> — sessão, 15 min</li>
            <li><code>refresh_token</code> — renovação, 30 dias</li>
          </ul>
          <p style="margin-top:10px">Ambos são <strong>HttpOnly</strong> — invisíveis ao JavaScript, apenas para autenticação.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>Base legal</h3>
          <p>Tratamos seus dados com base em <strong>execução de contrato</strong> (RGPD Art. 6(1)(b)) — são necessários para fornecer o serviço.</p>
          <div class="no-share">
            <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="4.93" y1="4.93" x2="19.07" y2="19.07"/></svg>
            Sem publicidade ou venda de dados
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Seus direitos -->
      <p class="section-label">Seus direitos (RGPD)</p>
      <div class="rights-grid">
        <div class="right-card">
          <div class="right-card-num">→</div>
          <div class="right-card-title">Portabilidade</div>
          <div class="right-card-desc">Exporte todos os seus dados em JSON a qualquer momento</div>
        </div>
        <div class="right-card">
          <div class="right-card-num">⊘</div>
          <div class="right-card-title">Esquecimento</div>
          <div class="right-card-desc">Delete sua conta — todos os dados pessoais são anonimizados</div>
        </div>
        <div class="right-card">
          <div class="right-card-num">↻</div>
          <div class="right-card-title">Retificação</div>
          <div class="right-card-desc">Seus dados são atualizados automaticamente via Google</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div class="privacy-actions" style="margin-top:20px">
        <a href="/account/export" class="btn btn-primary">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
          Exportar meus dados
        </a>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-ghost">Voltar</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
